==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dematerialize
<hw>De`ma*te"ri*al*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To
deprive of material or physical qualities or characteristics.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Dematerializing</qex> matter by stripping it of everything
which . . . has distinguished matter.</q>
<rj><qau>Milman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Deme</ent>⟦br⟧
